window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A novel about life and death and a quest for moral purpose, by the acclaimed author of word-of-mouth best seller <i>The First Fifteen Lives of Harry August</i>.</p> <p>Sooner or later, Death visits everyone. Before that, they meet Charlie: The Harbinger.</p> <p>Sometimes he comes as a courtesy, sometimes as a warning. Either way, this will be the most important meeting of your life.</p> <p>But who will come for Charlie?</p>"; 
